Funprog BACS_PRODATE_DETAIL(INCPY, SLIPNO, SLIDAT, SITE)
Value Char INCPY, SLIPNO, SITE
Value Date SLIDAT
Local Date PRODAT
Local Char RTN
Local Integer BANPRO

If clalev([HRFRMPAY])=0 : Local File HRFRMPAY [HRFRMPAY]  : Endif

Filter [HRFRMPAY] Where CPY = INCPY and NUMFRM = SLIPNO and DAT = SLIDAT and FCYFRM = SITE
